			  <td colspan=2 valign="top"><br>
		          <span class=msg>
                   I think you're out of luck.  The guy's only allowing port 80 to pass, so you'd have to capture those unusual port numbers that EQ uses, reroute them through 80, and then some external service would have to convert them back to the port number Sony is expecting. 
				  </span>
	          </td>
